=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Overviews_Operators_ex50 ===

DESCRIPTION: A bright pure_tone sound, with complex oscillator character around 1002 Hz, featuring very_slow attack and dynamic envelope, with dynamic spectral movement, energy distribution is late, filtered with resonant_steep_rolloff character, and spectrally simple.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: very_slow
  brightness: bright
  crest_factor_db: dynamic
  envelope_flatness: sustained
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: pure_tone
  spectral_complexity_mean: simple
  spectral_flux_normalized: dynamic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: late

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 1002.1316
  harmonic_decay_rate: -5.5431
  harmonic_regularity: 0.0908
  pitch_clarity: 254.2004
  inharmonicity: 0.0000
  type: complex
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -2.7536
  resonance_freq: 990.5273

